This paper discusses the coexistence of LTE and Wi-Fi technologies in unlicensed bands, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper also discusses the challenges and solutions related to information theory (cs.IT), system and control theory (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
